description: In Blackfield Brendon meets Anja, a former Nympha warrior, commander of an army of women. Anja is a fragile and fierce girl at the same time, desperately alone, and she profoundly affects the knight of venture. The woman, however, hides a secret: she is blackmailed by a wizard, Janus, that controls the life of his son and forces her to kill for him.
name: Lacrima di tenebra

description:
Collects : X-Force (1991) # 06 - X-Factor (1986) # 73, 74

06 - Toad's Brotherhood teams up with the Morlocks to take down X-Force. Stryfe continues to plot in the background.

73 - It's a mob running rampant through Washington, D.C. causing massive chaos!

74 - Introducing Slab, a new villian that goes one on one with Guido. Plus, more on the mysterious Madroxes.

It's time of elections at East City. Legs , Nathan , Al and Andy must protect Joseph Houseman , candidate for governor against the former mayor  Hoenzoller . After a bloody attack against Houseman , an illegal Memobox is found inside Houseman's brain, implanted sixty years before , when he was a cadet at the Space Infantry . Through the journalist Emma Key, Nathan comes into possession of the secret code of the Memobox of a dead reminder: it is the same code of Houseman's implant. And obscure secrets about Houseman past come to light.
name: La cortina del silenzio

description:
Collects : X-Force (1991) # 07, 08 - X-Factor (1986) # 75

07 - X-Force battles the Brotherhood. Sauron draws first blood. Elsewhere, Kane is ambushed by MLF in an extra story called "X-Tenuating Circumstances."

08 - Witnessing Cannonball's death, Cable has a flashback of his old team, the then Wild Pack. He also learns of a special condition Cannonball may have while in his present, the future. Out of his reverie, Cable shoots Sauron and shoots to kill.

Includes two Cable art pieces by Rob Liefeld.

75 - X-Factor reaches its 75th issue, and this double-size edition introduces the new super-villian team, The Nasty Boys. Meanwhile, X-Factor goes before the Senate to defend their very existance. Also: the plans of Ricochet and Mr. Sinister are revealed.
name: Vittime di Guerra

description:
Collects : X-Force (1991) # 09, 10 - X-Factor (1986) Annual # 07

09 - Cable tries to save Sam while the rest of X-Force fights the Brotherhood. In the end, it turns out Sam lives.

Kane battles the MLF and is confronted by Stryfe.

10 - Kane fights MLF and Stryfe reveals to Kane that he is Cable. X-Force deals with the fall-out of their fight with the Morlocks and the Brotherhood. Sam deals with learning he's an External. Behind the scenes, the Externals plan the acquisition of the newest mutant to "ascend."

X-Factor Annual 7 - Includes three stories: "Shattershot, Part Three," "Drowning in Paperwork," and "Cal and Guido."

Collects : X-Force (1991) # 11 - X-Factor (1986) # 77, 78

11 - Cable and the members of X-Force bring the bodies of Masque and Sauron to the Morlocks. Feral also has Thornn strapped in chains. She lets her sister gone with a warning as well as Cable's warning to the Morlocks.

Meanwhile, at the X-Force Base in the Adirondack Mountains, Deadpool sneaks into the X-Force base and attacks Domino, only, that's not really Domino...

Elsewhere, G. W. is hearing from Kane about his confrontation with the Mutant Liberation Front and Cable. At that point G.W. now wants to stop Cable and sends in Weapon Prime to take care of the problem.

In Austria it is shown that Domino is captured by Mr. Tolliver.

77 - Stryfe and his Mutant Liberation Front attack X-Factor and free the Nasty Boys. Later, Cannonball shows up to "liberate" Rahne from the control of the government. Rahne, however, is making friends, and Polaris proves it by letting Cannonball escape the questioning Havok has planned.

78 - The MLF attack again, but his time it's on a clinic in Kansas City, Missouri. X-Factor is too late to save the doctor; what of his research? The morals of Rahne and Quicksilver get in the way of completing this mission, and future mutants may thank them. Also, Mr. Sinister reclaims his Nasty Boys from Stryfe.
name: Domino Smascherata

description: Miah Redstone belatedly makes plans to attend her nephew’s bris when she learns that his circumcision has been cancelled. But will someone in the family have a change of heart? In the meantime, a rash of circumstraint thefts from California hospitals has the news media buzzing, and Miles Hastwick celebrates the opening of his new Brit Milah exhibit at the Museum of Genital Integrity.

Collects : X-Force (1991) # 12, 13 - X-Factor (1986) # 79

12 - After a brief battle, Gideon sends Crule to attack X-Force and bring in the newest External, Cannonball. Weapon Prime prepares to battle X-Force.

13 - Weapon Prime and X-Force have a long battle. Cable rigs his base to blow so SHIELD can't have access to his computers. Gideon experiments on Sunspot.

79 - Quicksilver and Multiple Man try to rescue a mutant that uses music as a power source. Sadly, she is very much insane.
name: Disastro !

description:
Collects : X-Force (1991) # 14 - X-Factor (1986) # 80, 81

14 - Cable's base has been blown up and Cable wants Tolliver's head, the man that has been in the shadows causing trouble. Cable and "Domino" are split up from the rest of X-Force. X-Force defeats Weapon Prime and are then attacked by SHIELD. Crule comes after Cannonball. Cable finds the real Domino held prisoner by Tolliver and Deadpool.

80 - X-Factor must protect an informant from the mutant drug dealers known as Hell's Belles.

81 - X-Factor manages to defeat the menace of the Hell's Belles, but meets a greater evil...the Brotherhood Of Evil Mutants!

Collects : X-Force (1991) # 15 - X-Factor (1986) # 82, 83

15 - Crule is dispatched and X-Force stages a rescue of Sunspot. Cable and Deadpool face off and Domino is freed. Tolliver finally gets his.

82 - X-Factor battles Toad's Brotherhood of Evil Mutants.

83 - Cameron Hodge, Sauron - can it be true? Have two of the deadliest X-Men villains returned seemingly from the grave to plague mankind, or is there something else amiss?
name: Solo uno Sopravviverà

description:
Collects : X-Men (1991) # 15 - X-Force (1991) # 17 - Uncanny X-Men (1963) # 296

X-Men 15 - Cyclops and Jean Grey continue being tormented by Stryfe (who clearly has some parental issues). Even worse, their powers have been dampened. On earth, Wolverine, Cable, and Bishop find that fleeing Department K will prove harder than they originally thought. And, the MLF finally gets taken down in Arkansas by a combined task force of X-Men, X-Factor, and X-Force. All the while, Xavier neither progresses or digresses.

X-Force 17 - Stryfe finds and defeats Apocalypse. The Dark Riders bow to him and swear allegiance to Stryfe.

Bishop and Wolverine are briefed on Graymalkin about Stryfe and the MLF and the events so far since the attempt on Xavier's life. Cable tells them about the Clan Chosen, his time traveling, and the fact that he and Stryfe are mysteriously identical.

Meanwhile, X-Force is locked up in the Danger Room. Siryn learns she was in love with one of Madrox's dupes, not the real one.

Jean Grey and Cyclops escape from the cell Stryfe had them detained in after learning he was dampening their powers.

Beast is trying to find a way to eliminate the T-O virus from Xavier when a beat up Apocalypse shows up at the X-Mansion offering his services.

U. X-Men 296 - Beast completes surgery on Professor X to remove Stryfe's bullet. Moira tells Beast she broke Stryfe's code in the T-O virus but it only says "You are smart but I am smarter" over and over. Apocalypse, detained in the X-Mansion, suggests that he can save Xavier and Archangel vouches for him.

Meanwhile, Stryfe's torture of Cyclops and Jean Grey continues. He presents them with an infant and tells them they if they destroy the child, they will destroy him as well. To Stryfe's amazement, they choose to rescue the child.

Cable uses the Professor to find Stryfe on Earth and comes to the conclusion that he's not on the planet.
name: Excuzione Parte 3

description:
Iris is back, but will she survive - The Hit List Agenda!!

Following the shocking cliffhanger ending to the critically acclaimed first volume, Executive Assistant Iris is ramping up the excitement and intrigue as this action-packed introductory zero issue kicks start an entirely new landscape of exotic locales and of course--Executive Assistants! With Mr. Ching, the ruthless corporate power-monger now out of the picture, a new cast of characters vie to take control of his empire. Yet, an even greater evil will rise up from the ashes of Ching’ s legacy, and this time, their reach is global! And by far the most important question of all is still a mystery—just what

happened to Iris?!?
name: Welcome to the Machine

description:
Collects : X-Force (1991) # 19, 20 - X-Factor (1986) # 87

19 - X-Force gets new costumes thanks to Boomer. While at the X-Mansion, Professor X tries to convince Cannonball that X-Force is going the wrong way in handling mutant peace.

20 - Graymalkin is uncovered during a Stark Industries satellite launch and the find brings SHIELD knocking to Cable's old base of operations. X-Force, upon finally getting communications set up in Camp Verde, see the station and teleport. The team finds a familiar voice in Professor, but the reunion with Ship is short-lived, as SHIELD has breached the base.

87 - This is one of the most critically and fan acclaimed issues of X-Factor. Get to know the team from the inside out as each member is interviewed by Doc Samson, psychologist to the super-hero community. Ever wonder why Quicksilver has a short fuse? Find out in this informative, albeit humorous, issue.
name: Il Sogno....Diviso

description:
Collects : X-Force (1991) # 21 - X-Factor (1986) # 88, 89

21 - War Machine is brought in by SHIELD to take out X-Force. X-Force puts up a good fight and wins. At Camp Verde, Siryn, Warpath, and Boomer are captured by the Externals. Like all of Cable's bases, Graymalkin blows up.

88 - Two stories: X-Factor battles Random for the rights of the X-Patriots in "Random Violence." Quicksilver and his wife (the Inhuman Crystal) have a couple getaway in the country in "Time Out."

89 - Two stories: X-Factor accompanies the X-Patriots back to Genosha in "Dark Homecoming." Quicksilver and Crystal try to rekindle their marriage in "Cabin Fever."
name: War Machine

description:
Collects : X-Force (1991) # 22, 23 - X-Factor (1986) # 90

22 - Both X-Force and SHIELD make it back to Earth, while Cannonball and Sunspot travel via a space pod. The team looks over the cache of weapons they recovered from Graymalkin. Domino and Grizzly meet resistance at Department K as they try to find Cable. X-Force finds out that Warpath, Siryn, and Boomer are captured by the Externals.

23 - Rictor, Shatterstar, Sunspot, and Feral find Crule so they can find the missing X-Force members. Domino fights Weapon Prime with the help of Grizzly and Hammer. She then finds Copycat and learns how to find Cable's old team. X-Force defeats the Externals and tells them to never mess with X-Force again.

90 - X-Factor is in Genosha and finds that most the mutates have contracted the Legacy Virus.

The shapeshifting mutant and bodyguard to the Genoshan President, Piecemeal, makes his debut. Thats him on the cover with a hole in the middle.

Wolfsbane is emotionally distraught over what was done to her in Genosha and lashes out at Polaris and Moira.
name: L'ultimo Dono

description: An eco-terrorist detained at the  Kingdom Hospital for tests , escapes , taking with him the young Kia Gibson as an hostage . Nathan Never and May Frayn are hired by Kia 's mother to find her daughter . The agents put themselves on the trail of the terrorist , but also the sinister Professor Trenton , director of the Kingdom Hospital, wants his proisoner back and puts a professional killer on the same trail.
name: Verso la libertà

description: Dr. Deville , a scientist who studies the nature of the universe, hires Nathan to guarantee the security of a space mission on an asteroid passing at short distance from the Earth . Led by space pirates Blackbeard and the Caribbean , Deville and his team intend to take possession of the mysterious "Lady of Ice ", a giant diamond with  undiscovered powers .
name: La dama di ghiaccio

description:
Collects : X-Force (1991) # 24 - X-Factor (1986) # 91, 93

24 - X-Force frees Rusty and Skids from the Friends of Humanity. Domino agrees to work with Copycat to find X-Force.

91 - X-Factor battles Armageddon in a final blow-out! Also: new Gengenineer Sasha Ryan's true agenda is revealed -- to rid the Earth of mutantkind altogether!

93 - Havok and Rahne visit Professor Xavier's School for the Gifted to pay their condolences for the loss of one of their members (see Uncanny X-Men #303 for the death of Ilyanna, the sister of Colossus). Meanwhile, an old friend takes Guido for a trip to the far side of the universe, and Val has just assigned a new member to the team.
name: Prigionieri del Fato

description: The eventful life of the Old Boy is further complicated by a series of sudden and unexplained illnesses . According to doctors it is just a little stress , but it soon becomes clear that there is mysterious hand plotting in the shadows: animated by a fierce sense of revenge, he enjoys sticking pins in a deadly wax doll that faithfully reproduces the appearance of the investigator of n ightmare .
name: Il sortilegio

description:
Collects : X-Force (1991) # 26, 27, 28

26 - Cable is healing from the fight with Magneto. His downtime is spent analyzing the motives of each team member. Reignfire breaks the MLF out of prison and reforms the team with a sinister plot.

27 - Reignfire makes his move against Henry Peter Gyrich. In taking the man captive, the MLF sees the new techno-organic contructs the government is working on. X-Force is the only unit that can take the assignment, so they attack the new MLF base. Their hopes of rescuing Gyrich is thrown a monkey wrench when they realize that a former friend has aligned herself with Reignfire.

28 - Reignfire proves to be pretty powerful and roughs up X-Force. Shatterstar cuts off one of Reaper's hands again. Riegnfire tries to turn Feral on her team and proves successful. Sunspot vanishes due to Lucus's teleport.

Collects : X-Force (1991) # 29, 30 - X-Factor (1986) # 94

29 - Arcade sets up Shatterstar to fight the Cadre Alliance and then X-Treme in Murderworld. Meanwhile, Cable sees a very fragile team around him and calls Domino in to help.

30 - After fighting, Shatterstar and X-Treme team up to take down Arcade. Juggernaut and Black Tom are back in Ireland, just in time for Siryn to make a visit. Domino arrives at Camp Verde to help reunite X-Force.

Note: X-Treme and Shatterstar first met in X-Force Annual #2. Also, Mr. Milbury was supposed to be Mr. Sinister, but this storyline was never furthered. (Adam X was supposed to be a rumored third Summers brother, something Sinister would be very interested in knowing.)

94 - Havok and Polaris confront a bigot against mutants at a restaurant and Random decides he will attack Polaris.

Dylan and Becky meet in a period of extreme difficulty for the girl , and it is immediately clear that their relationship could not be a textbook about love .  
After yet another dispute Dylan goes away , determined to never come back , yet in spite of himself he's back to where they started .
For him it's the beginning of a nightmare in which he will be forced to move at the pace of a shrimp , in search for the truth about himself and the mystery that Becky brings.
name: La seconda occasione

description: Brett Balsey is a good guy , serious , modest , habitual, reliable ... that is, terribly boring . H is routine is disrupted by  Ilyana , a mysterious and beautiful girl from Eastern Europe, in  London in search of well-being and safety . The two soon plan a  wedding, but soon Brett falls into the suspicion that his wife is not who she claims to be . To complicate things , Ilyana 's paraents unexpectedly arrive to London , in a frenetic succession of absurdities and. .. in the odor of sulfur .
name: Tra moglie e marito

description:
Collects : X-Force (1991) # 31, 35 - Excalibur (1988) # 72, 73

31 - In Ireland, Siryn and Warpath take a holiday, but Siryn only fills her time with more drinking. Warpath enlists an old friend of Siryn's to get her help. An alliance is made between Warpath and Juggernaut, as each only wants what is best for their friends. In the end, Black Tom's origin is discussed and both he and Siryn are able to get a little closure.

35 - X-Force finds out about a government project to create advanced artificial intelligence the likes of which weren't supposed to be seen until the future. Siryn asks Banshee for information on Nimrod. Cable lets Forge and X-Factor know about whats happening. After some reconnaissance, X-Force break into a facility at Camp Hayden to thwart the project and are quickly defeated by an awakened Nimrod.

Note: There is an error on page 15. In a discussion about Siryn's run-in with Black Tom, as well as about X-Force stealing files from the X-Men, an asterisk points the reader to X-Force #19, as if both events happened in the same book. In truth, X-Force stole the files in #19 while Siryn met with Black Tom in #31.

72

73
name: X-Universe

description:
Collects : X-Factor (1986) # 101, 102 - X-Force (1991) # 36 - Excalibur (1988) # 74

101 - X-Factor mourns the death of a core member! Havok comes to terms with his guilt over the loss of a teammate, while Rahne confronts her fears about death...since this is not the first time she has lost a friend in battle.

102 - When X-Factor begins an investigation the government wants stopped, the team is forced into a confrontation with members of Freedom Force.

36 - Cable and X-Force fight Nimrod and use logic to defeat the Sentinel. Cable's techno-virus flares up. The Externals return.

74 -
name: Nuova Vita

description:
Collects : X-Factor (1986) # 103, 104, 105 - X-Force (1991) # 37

103 - Guido, Rahne, and Random go out for night on the town. Meanwhile, Havok and Polaris attempt to recapture their romance in Hawaii. But this will be a difficult task, because the mind altering menace of Malice has returned!

104 - The non-corporal Malice, the very villainess who enslaved Polaris for years, has now taken control of Havok. Awwww...and the two ex-lovers were just getting along so nicely. Plus, what will happen when Mr. Sinister and his Nasty Boys show up?

105 - It's Polaris vs. Malice vs. Havok vs. Mr. Sinister and the Nasty Boys...not everyone is walking away from this one alive.

37 - Everything you want to know about the Externals. Sam and Tabitha show their feelings for each other.
name: Sacrificio Finale

description:
Collects : X-Force (1991) # 39, 40 - Excalibur (1988) # 81, 83

39 - Prosh comes to X-Force and turns out he is Cable's computer system, Professor, given a body when a Phalanx loses its mind when connected to X-Force's computers. Cable's Techno-virus is going out of control because Prosh drains the power that keeps Cable alive. It is decided that Prosh must go, but to do so he must take the network and much of the base.

40 - Lucia Callasantos (Thornn) is hunted down by New York's finest for the murder of her family. Declaring innocence, she turns to X-Force to help prove that it was her sister Maria (Feral) who actually committed the murders. They lure Feral to the old home of the Callasantos family in hopes of finally getting some answers.

81 - Captain Britain recounts his trek through the timestream to Meggan and is happy to be back with her. Kitty tries to talk about old times with the New Mutants with Douglock who is not receptive. She gets upset that he's not the Doug Ramsey she knew and storms out.

Meanwhile in Paris, Xavier and Moira are at the Eiffel Tower and Moira begins to get emotional about dying. Xavier made reservations at a fancy restaurant and Moira gets upset that she's not dressed for the occasion.

Back on Muir Island, Meggan makes Braddock feel better about the insignificance of their lives relative to the entirety of the timesteam. Meanwhile at the pub, Kitty gets into a bar fight and knocks a guy out.

Xavier telepathically makes the people in the restaurant think they're well dressed famous people and Moira cracks up laughing. They go to Notre Dame and make out and laugh.

83 - The Soulsword was the consummate expression of Illyana Rasputin's arcane might. When she succumbed to the Legacy Virus, the Soulsword bonded to her best friend, Kitty Pryde. Now, Kitty is being driven insane by the weapon, and her friends in Excalibur search for a way to help her. Meanwhile, two new foes enter the fray, both with agendas all their own.
name: La Spada dell'anima

description:
Collects : X-Factor (1986) # 110 - X-Force (1991) # 41 - Excalibur (1988) # 84, 85

110 - When Lila Cheney returns to Earth with a new task at hand, how exactly is X-Factor involved, and what effect will it have on Guido?

41 - Feral and Thornn's past are brought to light as X-Force and the sisters track through the old house in the Bronx. The sisters show how they became hardened and just who exactly is responsible for the deaths of each member of their family.

84 - When the sorcerer Gravemoss takes possession of Nightcrawler and visits Muir Island, Excalibur is at a loss to explain the strange occurences besieging Moira MacTaggert's facility. Meanwhile, the sorceress Shrill confronts Kitty Pryde with the intentions of killing her, to prevent her from ever drawing the Soulsword, again.

85 - The events of the Soul Sword Trilogy reach an explosive climax as Gravemoss, still possessing Nightcrawler, faces off against Kitty Pryde, Shrill, and Daytripper for control of the Soulsword.

Stories included:

The Walking Dead
The Uninvited Corpse
The Phantom Killer
The Curse of Sika
The Shrunken Heads of Dr. Death
name: Beware of the Uninvited Corpse

description:
Collects : X-Factor (1986) # 111 - X-Force (1991) # 42, 43 - Excalibur (1988) # 86

111 - Lila Cheney's troubles mount as X-Factor attempts to stop an alien invasionthat threatens to destroy the entire planet. And Mystique is caught off guard, which could mean the end for her -- for real -- this time!

42 - Warpath learns the Hellfire Club was not responsible for the butchering of his people. He also has a candid talk with Emma Frost about his motives for staying with X-Force. Meanwhile, Siryn talks about her feelings for Warpath with her father, Banshee.

43 - Running Cerebro and Cable's Time Chamber simultaneously, Cannonball locates Sunspot. Oddly enough, Locus appears and teleports X-Force away in order to stop Sunspot from doing something awful. X-Force arrives at the MLF camp to find that Sunspot has supposedly been around all along as the terrorist Reignfire. The finding comes to late, as reality is ripped apart and the Age of Apocalypse begins.

86 - Britanic fixes up Moiras hovercraft. There are reports of violence in genosha and excalibur is asked to investigate a type of weapon that kills mutants. The plane gets hit by a mistle and starts to go down.
name: La Fine

description: Two girls without a  past a fight for their freedom. A prostitution ring hides a tragic reality : genetics offers new roads to the horror ...
name: La città del vizio

description:
Outta the way – It's the "Flash" issue!

It's the fastest comic ever and the race is on! This special issue introduces Jessie Quick and features Inertia and Mas y Menos. Plus: Kid Flash sharpens his pencil to a FLASHPOINT! Plus plus: Blue Beetle makes a special appearance!
name: The Fast issue! The Fastest Comic Ever!

description: Nathan leaves for a vacation with her daughter Ann in the Protected Area , on the beach of Saint Mary . The thief Miss Mawby , to avoid being captured by the mutate Jefferson , gives accidentally to Nathan a Shanachies Circle, an artifact that allows father and daughter to have a vision of their future.
name: Visioni dal futuro

description: In ancient times , the high priests of Babylon was given custody of the secret of a race of speaking reptiles , the Venerable s, who then disappeared . At the time of Nathan Never , Sarah Leclerc requests the intervention of the Alfa Agency to find his father Abraham , an anthropologist who disappeared in the second level of the City. From his diary we learn that the man , during an exploration , found in the basement of the Central City Hospital, a walled room with decorations of Babylonian origin...
name: Il segreto di Babilonia

description: Who is behind the Global Research , a company that can change at will the weather ? Alfa Agency tries to shed light on the issue.
name: Minaccia dal cielo
